  "description": "Plans for 2025-03-28:\npost to @michael-marmot@HIVE about birds soaking their bread in the creek. Remake Sigmund Vexler\u0026rsquo;s HIVE account Make sigmund@561.group email Register via Ecency, using Michael Marmot\u0026rsquo;s referral link write a new introduction post Setup Sigmund\u0026rsquo;s Sat Stacker Swap Bitcoin Lightning for Base Ethereum via SwapSpace to Sigmund Vexler\u0026rsquo;s Ethereum wallet Setup Sat Stacker vault on DexFi. Transfer emsenn\u0026rsquo;s spare liquidity into the Sat Stacker Vault from emsenn\u0026rsquo;s Based DeFi Vault Setup Sigmund\u0026rsquo;s Liquid Vault on Hive Register via Ecency, using Sigmund\u0026rsquo;s referral link Transfer in liquidity from michael561, essiebee, marshian Allocate into liquidity pools ¶About the birds There’s a little creek behind the apartment. Not much to look at—runs between some chainlink and a parking lot, mostly hidden unless you know to listen for it. I didn’t move here for the view. Moved here for family reasons, and figured I’d be closer to pavement than water for the foreseeable future.\n",
